task1. Create a clock with stop and start.

task2. Modify your calculator to listen to keyboard events
+, -, 1, 2, 3, 4, 5 ..., =, /, *, backslash, C

task3. Create a simple login form with email input, password input, and submit button. After submit button click
you should validate email and password.
Validation 1. The email must be a valid email (example@example.com)
Validation 2. The password must be more than 12 characters length and must include a digit, 
an upper case letter and a special symbol.
If the form is not valid you should alert it to user. If the form is valid you should console.log email and password.
